            <h3>Features</h3>
            <ul class="features-list">
              <li>User registration & login (JWT)</li>
              <li>Stores all URLs + user search history</li>
              <li>FastAPI backend + SQLAlchemy ORM storage</li>
              <li>Full custom frontend UI built from scratch</li>
            </ul>
